 <metadata>
  <name>Running Warehouse Marathon and Federation University Half Marathon</name>
  <desc>This course has it all: autumn colours, beautiful scenery and historic buildings. And for 2025 it's flatter, faster and more fun, with the uphill finish removed in favour of a u-turn on historic Lydiard Street.</desc>
  <author>
   <name>Adam McNicol</name>
   <link href="https://www.strava.com/athletes/112990563"/>
